This object specifies the spanning tree BPDU Guard Mode. enable(1) - enables BPDU Guard Mode on the switch. disable(2) - disables BPDU Guard Mode on the switch. The default status is disabled.

This object specifies the spanning tree BPDU Filter Mode, it enables BPDU Filter on all edge ports. enable(1) - enables BPDU Filter Mode on the switch. disable(2) - disables BPDU Filter Mode on the switch. The default status is disabled.
